name: Shoulda Bought More
description: More is a meme coin that plays on the universal feeling of 'I should’ve bought more', the regret that often strikes when people look at the price chart of a token they were underexposed to. The token captures this sense of missed opportunity, becoming a symbol for those who feel they didn’t invest enough when the market was at a favorable price. More resonates with investors who have experienced the frustration of seeing a token’s value rise after they missed the chance to buy in earlier.
